E4Extra.uk.title: Couples Come Dine with Me
E4Extra.uk.description: In Durham, Steph and James serve gastropub grub, but can they avoid falling out? Gary and Amanda's pig joins their party. And on the final night, the guests discover Andy's reward chart!

E4Extra.uk.title: Couples Come Dine with Me
E4Extra.uk.description: In South Wales, Rachael and Nick cook dishes they've never made before, Ameel shows off his powers of memory recall, and Angela bosses Jeff around as they prepare their no-nonsense menu.

E4Extra.uk.title: Couples Come Dine with Me
E4Extra.uk.description: In Swansea and Bridgend, the competition includes terrible table manners and tactless banter, chicken lettuce boats, kitchen chaos - and a final showdown at the dinner table.

E4Extra.uk.title: Couples Come Dine with Me
E4Extra.uk.description: In Blackpool, ex-dancer Rowan and businessman John take on hard-to-please Holly and Ollie, and Sally and Joanne, who wear matching tie-dye, in a week featuring a belly-busting breakfast.

E4Extra.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Extra.uk.description: Zayna Flaming Grill (Part 1/2): Gordon makes the first of two visits to Zayna Flaming Grill, a Mediterranean restaurant in Redondo Beach owned by Faye and her niece Brenda. (S7 Ep6)

E4Extra.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Extra.uk.description: Zayna Flaming Grill (Part 2/2): Gordon returns to California for the conclusion of his challenge to save Zayna Flaming Grill. Can he inject flavour into the tired menu? (S7 Ep7)

E4Extra.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Extra.uk.description: Bella Luna: Gordon visits Italian family restaurant Bella Luna, which is struggling with an inexperienced chef and an owner who won't acknowledge the eatery's flaws. (S7 Ep8)

E4Extra.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Extra.uk.description: Gordon Ramsay revisits three restaurants he's helped: La Galleria 33 in Boston; The Olde Hitching Post in Massachusetts; and the Prohibition Grille in Washington. (S7 Ep9)

E4Extra.uk.title: Taskmaster's Bleeped New Year...
E4Extra.uk.description: ...Treat: With just three points separating the celebs, it's all to play for in the second leg. Big Zuu gets competitive with a shoe. And can Susie Dent make Alex's dream come true? (Ep2/2)

E4Extra.uk.title: Big Fat Quiz of Everything 2025
E4Extra.uk.description: Harry Hill, David Mitchell, Roisin Conaty, Sophie Willan, Josh Pugh and Fatiha El-Ghorri tackle Jimmy Carr's comprehensive quiz, from Henry VIII to the first meme and lots more in between!

E4Extra.uk.title: 8 Out of 10 Cats Does Countdown
E4Extra.uk.description: Jimmy Carr hosts as Sean Lock and Jason Manford take on guest captain Sarah Millican and Jonathan Ross. Bill Bailey joins Susie Dent in Dictionary Corner. (S6 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch Michael McIntyre's The Wheel, Love Is Blind, Strictly Come Dancing, Boiling Point, HELP! My House Is Haunted, and All Creatures Great and Small. (S22 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The TV shows include Big Brother: The Launch, Don't Look Down for SU2C, Antiques Roadshow, Coronation Street, Big Little Journeys and Beat the Chasers Celebrity Special. (S22 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Open House: The Great Sex...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Experiment: Married couple Al and Jasmine have dabbled in sex parties before, but now want to take things further. Alex and Lydie want to push their boundaries even more... (S1 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: A celebration of Naked Attraction's very best naughty bits, revisiting some bad romances, from arguments to cringeworthy moments, including Cathy and Andy's explosive reunion.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Billion Pound Cruise
